      "description": "Budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left for the right owner. Starts, runs, and offers a solid opportunity for a cheap commuter, project car, or handy backup vehicle. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but if you want affordable wheels without spending a fortune, this one is worth a look. Priced to move and ready for someone who can give it a little TLC.",
