    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-focused project with solid enthusiast bones and plenty of upside. The powertrain fires up and runs, the chassis feels fundamentally usable, and it has the kind of honest, mechanical character that makes it a great candidate for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. Not a showpiece, but a straightforward platform with good parts value, strong project potential, and the right kind of wear for a budget-minded build, daily beater, or weekend revival. Priced accordingly for its condition and ready for its next owner to take it the rest of the way.",
